text: Bassirou Diomaye Faye (born 25 March 1980) is a Senegalese politician and former tax inspector, who is the 5th President of Senegal since 2024. He is the former general secretary of dissolved PASTEF and won the 2024 presidential election. Faye has two wives; Marie Khone Faye and Absa Faye. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1980 births Category:Presidents of Senegal Category:Current national leaders
